title: MoWAS2 Red Rising 3.2.2
description:
How to install:
    1)Extract 7z file.
    2)Drag the Red Rising folder into your Men of War Assault Squad 2 Mods folder.
    3)Go to the options menu in the game and select MODS
    4)Activate the mod

Updating Manually:
 If the mod does not work with your version of MoWAS2 game.
    1)Open your Red Rising folder in your mods folder
    2)Openwith notepad
    3)Edit {MaxGameVersion "3.252.0"} line, change the version number to latest version (If you are using older version change the MinGameVersion instead
